Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:22.56,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}Who sings this song about us pain and sorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:30.78,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}鏡映しの業を　済ましたふり繕って　見つめてた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.78,0:01:36.33,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}繰り返す痛み　未だ知らぬ憧れ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:40.96,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}The weight of my sin nails me down　足搔いても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:46.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}Is it the future falling　偶像崇拝みたいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:51.84,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}微かな不安の足音を　Despair of all
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:56.89,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}Emptiness follows you here　This never-ending war
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.89,0:02:01.98,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}信じたい未来へ　巻き戻して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.98,0:02:09.19,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}赦せなくて　escalateして　escalateして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:12.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}I need someone to 目を伏せ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.95,0:02:20.29,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}Pray in my name　太古へ祈って　折れては繋いで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:25.04,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}Again and again and again　螺旋のよう　one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:30.51,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}何故戦い続けるの？　まだ捨てきれない物は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:38.35,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}仮初めか確かな希望か　ふれる針
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:22.56,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}谁在吟咏我们的痛与伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:30.78,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}镜中映射的罪业  虚假的救赎  历历在目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.78,0:01:36.33,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}反反复复的伤痛  虚无缥缈的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.33,0:01:40.96,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}罪业之重令我难以喘息  挣扎只是徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:46.50,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}是否这就是未来崩坏  如同偶像崇拜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:51.84,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}那微弱且不安的脚步声  传递出对一切的绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:56.89,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}虚无已经找到你了  这没有尽头的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.89,0:02:01.98,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}倒带回想要去相信的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.98,0:02:09.19,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}无法原谅  怒火在上升  在不断上升
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:12.95,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}我需要人们将目光转过去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.95,0:02:20.29,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}以我之名祈祷  向太古祈祷  重铸盟约
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:25.04,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}不论世间轮回  宛如无穷螺旋  终重复一事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:30.51,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}为何不停战斗？  而这仍未割舍之物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:38.35,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur3}究竟是南柯一梦还是希望之花 指针癫狂地转动着
